item.title: CVE-2023-2224|2023-06-05T13:39:02.151Z -- unknown -- seo%20by%2010web
item.description: The SEO by 10Web WordPress plugin before 1.2.7 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup).
